She looked at Kluster. " I...I want to thank you for showing me the 
way to your leader.  This meeting with the other group leaders is so 
important.  If you want, I can invite another to acompany your leader 
to the embacy.  I want to show that we mean no harm and that we are 
truely working for peace among all the groups."  She smiled.  "just 
think, you could run across the continant and not get attacked.  
Wouldn't it be wonderful?"
